      <a href="https://orangette.net/2004/12/two-years/#comment-71460"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2019-01-31T15:41:56-05:00">Thursday, January 31, 2019 at 3:41 pm</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I’m reading your book and I’m at the part where you write about your father’s illness.  It’s very moving and I have to be careful where I read it &#8211; the tears start rolling down my cheek.  This is a very loving tribute to your father.  Beautifully written.</p>
    </div>

